_sText:
This map was original released for the game Day of Defeat: Source. It received positive feedback so we decided to modify it and develop it for Counter-Strike: Source as well. This map can be a GunGame map. This map does feature BuyZones for both teams. There is a total of 44 spawn points (22 for Counter-Terrorists and 22 for Terrorists). 

If you have any comments, ideas, or suggestions please message us.

Thank you for your time.
